  m_text: "As a mechanics developer, you are the first point of contact for mechanical
    elements. You develop the mechanical architecture of the system. Your competencies
    are mainly in finding and testing solutions and solution and function patterns.
    In doing so, you coordinate closely with electronics and software colleagues.
    Occasionally you also support colleagues on overarching issues.\u200B\n\nNumber
    of Resources available per round: 9"
