  m_text: 'As a software developer, you are responsible for implementing the information
    technology system functions. You coordinate the mechanical and electronic components
    of the system to achieve the desired behaviour during operation. Accordingly,
    cooperation with these colleagues is essential. Occasionally, you also support
    colleagues in overarching issues.


    Number of Resources available per round:
    9'
