  m_text: "As a project manager, it is your task to collect and provide information
    and data of strategic importance. Furthermore, you are the contact person for
    internal and external stakeholders. As a leader, you support your team in all
    socio-technical issues.\v\r\n\nNumber of Resources available per round: 8"
