  m_text: 'As a product manager, your business skills make you primarily responsible
    for commercial issues. Doing so primarily shapes the value creation structure
    and the product strategy. The project manager provides you with the technical
    specifications. You can also support your colleagues in other socio-technical
    issues.


    Number of Resources available per round: 9'
