  m_text: 'As a systems architect, you are the head of technical development. It
    is your task to integrate the results of the domains into an overall solution
    and to ensure the functional safety of the system. You are the team''s contact
    person for technical questions. You often work closely with the project manager
    to balance technical and economic factors.


    Number of Resources available
    per round: 12'
